text: The Legislative Assembly of the Falkland Islands currently has two multi- member constituencies (). ==Constituencies== ===Current=== The two current constituencies are: * Camp (created in 1977) * Stanley (created in 1949) ===Former=== * East Falkland (1949-1985) * East Stanley (1977-1985) * West Falkland (1949-1985) * West Stanley (1977-1985) ==References== Falkland Islands
title: Constituencies of the Falkland Islands
